➜恐怖新选手！上市仅1年，上险量已超6.5万辆，长安欧尚X7第10万台下线
http://www.sohu.com/a/432452708_99994080	35501
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201117/8b449b043f2f4f319927562d2a0ae677.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201117/5105e147751642d5adc74a6a82ab2af8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201117/2d40d715410d4d749191b125bea4a038.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
